### Dependencies & Versions

| Package      | Version                |
| ------------ | ---------------------- |
| Python       | 3.13.5                 |
| Pandas       | 2.3.1                  |
| NumPy        | 2.3.1                  |
| Scikit-learn | 1.6.1                  |
| Streamlit    | 1.46.1                 |
| Pickle       | Built-in Python module |

### Installation

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### requirements.txt

```text
pandas==2.3.1
numpy==2.3.1
scikit-learn==1.6.1
streamlit==1.46.1
```
